#: page-investor-visa.php:26
msgid "Book Investor Visa Consultation"
msgstr ""

#: page-investor-visa.php:45
msgid "What Is an Investor KITAS?"
msgstr ""

#: page-investor-visa.php:47
msgid "An <strong>Investor KITAS</strong> is a type of KITAS (Kartu Izin Tinggal Terbatas – Temporary Stay Permit) issued specifically to foreign nationals who hold a valid <strong>shareholder position in a PT&nbsp;PMA</strong> (foreign-owned limited liability company) registered in Indonesia."
msgstr ""

#: page-investor-visa.php:50
msgid "Unlike a working KITAS — which requires a Work Permit (IMTA) from the Ministry of Manpower — the Investor KITAS is issued based on your registered investment position through the Indonesian Investment Coordinating Board (BKPM) and the Online Single Submission (OSS) system."
msgstr ""

#: page-investor-visa.php:53
msgid "This makes the Investor KITAS one of the most practical residency options for foreign entrepreneurs and business owners who want to live in and actively manage their business in Indonesia."
msgstr ""

#: page-investor-visa.php:57
msgid "<strong>💡 Key Point:</strong> You must have a PT&nbsp;PMA already registered — or set one up simultaneously — to qualify for an Investor KITAS. Our office can assist with both the company setup and the Investor KITAS application as a combined service."
msgstr ""

