#: page-kitap.php:44
msgid "<strong>KITAP</strong> (Kartu Izin Tinggal Tetap) is Indonesia's <strong>Permanent Stay Permit</strong> — the highest level of legal residency available to foreign nationals in Indonesia. Unlike KITAS (Temporary Stay Permit), KITAP allows you to reside in Indonesia on a long-term basis without needing annual renewals."
