msgid "<strong>KITAS</strong> (Kartu Izin Tinggal Terbatas) is a Temporary Stay Permit issued by the Indonesian Immigration Authority to foreign nationals who wish to reside in Indonesia for an extended period — typically for work, investment, or family reasons."
msgstr ""

#: page-kitas.php:47
msgid "A KITAS is not a visa, but a stay permit that is issued after entering Indonesia on the appropriate visa. It allows the holder to live legally in Indonesia for a specified period (usually 6 or 12 months) and is renewable annually."
