#: page-pt-pma.php:196
msgid "PT PMA Setup Process – Step by Step"
msgstr ""

#: page-pt-pma.php:198
msgid "Our lawyer manages the entire process across all government agencies — you focus on your business while we handle the legal and regulatory work."
msgstr ""

#: page-pt-pma.php:206
msgid "Legal Consultation &amp; Structure Planning"
msgstr ""

#: page-pt-pma.php:208
msgid "We review your business plan, intended KBLI (business activity code), sector eligibility under the Positive Investment List, proposed ownership structure, and capital allocation. We advise on the optimal legal structure before any registration begins."
msgstr ""

#: page-pt-pma.php:211
msgid "1–3 days"
msgstr ""

#: page-pt-pma.php:212
msgid "Our Office"
msgstr ""

#: page-pt-pma.php:222
msgid "We check the availability of your proposed company name and reserve it through the Ministry of Law and Human Rights (Kemenkumham) AHU Online system. We recommend preparing 2–3 name options in order of preference."
msgstr ""

#: page-pt-pma.php:225 page-pt-pma.php:281 page-pt-pma.php:309
msgid "1–3 business days"
msgstr ""

#: page-pt-pma.php:226
msgid "Kemenkumham AHU System"
msgstr ""

#: page-pt-pma.php:234
msgid "Articles of Association Drafting"
msgstr ""

#: page-pt-pma.php:236
msgid "We draft the Articles of Association (Anggaran Dasar) of the PT PMA, covering company name, registered address, business activities, share capital structure, shareholder details, director and commissioner appointments, and key governance provisions. This is the foundational legal document of your company."
msgstr ""

#: page-pt-pma.php:239
msgid "2–4 days"
msgstr ""

#: page-pt-pma.php:240
msgid "Our Office + Notary"
msgstr ""

#: page-pt-pma.php:248
msgid "Notarial Deed of Establishment (Akta Pendirian)"
msgstr ""

#: page-pt-pma.php:250
msgid "The Articles of Association are formalised before a licensed Indonesian notary (Notaris) as the Deed of Establishment (Akta Pendirian). All shareholders and directors must authorise this step — either in person, through a Power of Attorney, or via official representative. We coordinate the notary appointment and prepare all required documents."
msgstr ""

#: page-pt-pma.php:253
msgid "1–2 days (signing)"
msgstr ""

#: page-pt-pma.php:254
msgid "Licensed Notary Office"
msgstr ""

#: page-pt-pma.php:262
msgid "Ministry of Law Ratification (SK Kemenkumham)"
msgstr ""

#: page-pt-pma.php:264
msgid "The notary submits the deed to the Ministry of Law and Human Rights for official ratification as a legal entity (Badan Hukum). This step formally creates the PT PMA as a legal entity in Indonesia. The SK (Decision Letter) from Kemenkumham is issued once approved."
msgstr ""

#: page-pt-pma.php:267
msgid "5–10 business days"
msgstr ""

#: page-pt-pma.php:268
msgid "Kemenkumham (Ministry of Law)"
msgstr ""

#: page-pt-pma.php:276
msgid "OSS Registration &amp; NIB Issuance"
msgstr ""

#: page-pt-pma.php:278
msgid "We register the PT PMA through the Online Single Submission (OSS) system to obtain the NIB (Nomor Induk Berusaha — Business Identity Number). The NIB serves as the company's primary business registration number and is required for all subsequent licences and government reporting."
msgstr ""

#: page-pt-pma.php:282
msgid "OSS System (BKPM)"
msgstr ""

#: page-pt-pma.php:290
msgid "Business Licence &amp; Sector Permits"
msgstr ""

#: page-pt-pma.php:292
msgid "Depending on your business activity (KBLI code), additional sector-specific licences may be required from the relevant government ministry. We identify all required permits and manage the application process for each."
msgstr ""

#: page-pt-pma.php:295
msgid "1–4 weeks (varies by sector)"
msgstr ""

#: page-pt-pma.php:296
msgid "Relevant Ministry / OSS"
msgstr ""

#: page-pt-pma.php:304
msgid "NPWP Tax Registration"
msgstr ""

#: page-pt-pma.php:306
msgid "The company must be registered for a Tax Identification Number (NPWP — Nomor Pokok Wajib Pajak) with the Directorate General of Taxation (DJP). The NPWP is required before opening a bank account, hiring employees, or issuing invoices."
msgstr ""

#: page-pt-pma.php:318
msgid "Corporate Bank Account Opening"
msgstr ""

#: page-pt-pma.php:320
msgid "We assist with opening a corporate bank account at an Indonesian bank. This is required for capital injection, payroll, and business transactions. We provide a bank introduction letter and assist with the account opening documentation."
msgstr ""

#: page-pt-pma.php:323 page-pt-pma.php:337
msgid "1–2 weeks"
msgstr ""

#: page-pt-pma.php:324
msgid "Indonesian Commercial Bank"
msgstr ""

#: page-pt-pma.php:332
msgid "Capital Injection &amp; BKPM Reporting"
msgstr ""

#: page-pt-pma.php:334
msgid "The minimum paid-up capital (IDR 2.5 billion) must be transferred to the company bank account and evidenced for BKPM/OSS reporting. We prepare the capital injection documentation and set up your LKPM (Investment Activity Report) reporting schedule."
msgstr ""

#: page-pt-pma.php:338
msgid "Company Bank + OSS/BKPM"
msgstr ""

#: page-pt-pma.php:346
msgid "Investor KITAS Application (Optional)"
msgstr ""

#: page-pt-pma.php:348
msgid "Once the PT PMA is fully registered and the foreign shareholder's position is confirmed in OSS, we can proceed with the Investor KITAS application — allowing the foreign investor to legally reside in Indonesia as the company shareholder. We manage both processes simultaneously to reduce total setup time."
msgstr ""

#: page-pt-pma.php:351
msgid "3–6 weeks (concurrent with steps 6–10)"
msgstr ""

#: page-pt-pma.php:352
msgid "Indonesian Immigration Office"
msgstr ""

